props.name: ariaLabel
props.description: The text for the `aria-label` which labels the service navigation container when a service name is included.

props.name: menuButtonText
props.description: The text of the mobile navigation menu toggle.

props.name: menuButtonLabel
props.description: The screen reader label for the mobile navigation menu toggle. Defaults to the same value as `menuButtonText` if not specified.

props.name: navigationLabel
props.description: The screen reader label for the mobile navigation menu. Defaults to the same value as `menuButtonText` if not specified.

props.name: navigationId
props.description: The ID used to associate the mobile navigation toggle with the navigation menu.

props.name: navigationClass
props.description:
Classes to add to the navigation menu container.
You can bind a string, an array or an object, as with normal [Vue class bindings](https://vuejs.org/guide/essentials/class-and-style.html#binding-html-classes).

props.name: serviceNameLinkComponent
props.description: The component used to render the service name link, for example `RouterLink`. Will default to `a` if a `serviceUrl` is provided or no link otherwise.

slots.name: start
slots.description: Content injected at the start of the service header container

slots.name: end
slots.description: Content injected at the end of the service header container
